setup windows virtual machine
download iso
using virtio drivers: https://wiki.archlinux.org/title/QEMU#Using_virtio_drivers
Setup common files system
https://github.com/virtio-win/kvm-guest-drivers-windows/wiki/Virtiofs:-Shared-file-system#guest
https://fedorapeople.org/groups/virt/virtio-win/direct-downloads/archive-virtio/virtio-win-0.1.271-1/virtio-win-guest-tools.exe
more ref: https://virtio-fs.gitlab.io/howto-windows.html
